{"tid":384641,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人在大陸, 班蝗死衝爛衝笑撚死","createTime":"2017-09-02T12:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T16:17:32.000Z","uid":84267,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ebb2d9d85289cca7fc411e0dd57fc3be328c37f5","tid":384641,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:56:08.000Z","msg":"呢幾日同家人喺大陸玩. 咁今日就去左個商場. 我拍完車, 從停車場搭lift上去商場啦.<br />\n<br />\n一開lift, 出面就有幾個大陸佬鳩衝入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我同家人要喺呢層出wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁班撚樣大陸佬就因為鳩衝緊入黎阻撚住曬我地出唔到(喺佢地立場係我地阻住佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n<br />\n咁我本身不嬲有做gym, 比起班撚樣大陸佬大隻, 又咁啱我企前面, 所以我就挺起心口用力逼出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成班大陸佬被我撞到跌低, 咁我就好有禮貌咁講句: 不好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班大陸佬個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連平時都好鵪鶉既呀媽都笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d710c627506eceaeaab6421462f5c733892cfbe","tid":384641,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T13:03:49.000Z","msg":"仲有排隊個陣, D蝗好撚鐘意跟到貼一貼, 然後慢慢企你隔離, 繼而打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我對付呢D賤種既方法就係兩手叉腰等佢過唔到我, 企得我貼既話就擰轉身望佢順手問埋佢係咪gay佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa622de43036cb5dce52bcfcc9f787f147e632a","tid":384641,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T13:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70dffeeaf42e5bf9dc2806656c2ba32e1d781a6a","tid":384641,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef874238e6948a5c00393a44ced6890745a3c399","tid":384641,"uid":84267,"like":0,"d